title: [Idip Udip Wedip]
description: Crammed into the confines of this small space is a pair of armless maroon-on-jade jacquard silk upholstered chairs with a small oak table between them.  A long lacquered pine counter stretches from near the glass-paned door to the back wall, ending beside a skinny ladder leading up to the house's loft.
